01:09:46.359 --> 01:09:49.094
Well, Brigit went out,

01:09:49.395 --> 01:09:50.929
did some research.

01:09:53.031 --> 01:09:54.400
She started to think that...

01:09:55.368 --> 01:09:59.171
traveling musicians...
would be the answer,

