Let's trade!

01:14:10.956 --> 01:14:13.292
We'll give you free passes out.

01:14:14.694 --> 01:14:15.928
Just give us Kyle.

01:14:17.596 --> 01:14:19.197
We'll stand down.

01:14:21.934 --> 01:14:23.602
Give you my word.

01:14:26.372 --> 01:14:27.807
