the FBI boys to get here

01:14:30.276 --> 01:14:32.778
and I'll... I'll back everything
you say, I swear.

01:14:34.680 --> 01:14:35.815
Does the sheriff know
about Brigit?

01:14:36.649 --> 01:14:38.384
No, no.

01:14:38.417 --> 01:14:41.320
We keep the sheriff and Kyle
in the dark about everything.

01:14:41.821 --> 01:14:44.356
