No, no! Get me outta here.

01:17:57.082 --> 01:17:58.150
Fucking kidding me?

01:18:01.020 --> 01:18:02.154
Get this done.

01:18:02.621 --> 01:18:05.925
Kill them all, burn the lab.
FBI is 8 minutes out.

01:18:22.107 --> 01:18:23.075
Cut him loose, Roy.

01:18:25.044 --> 01:18:27.146
If we can get to the lab,
we may be able to hold them off.

01:18:43.296 --> 01:18:45.030
